# Pi 5 camera setting

白色面朝 HDMI 方向
蓝色 FPC 面朝 USB 方向
（Pi5 的 CSI 接口与 Pi4方向相反）

```
ls /dev/video*
vcgencmd get_camera

sudo apt update
sudo apt install libcamera-apps libcamera-tools -y


sudo apt install qv4l2 v4l-utils -y

rpicam-hello --timeout 5000
rpicam-still -o test.jpg
rpicam-vid -o test.h264 -t 10000

```

# GStreamer
```
gst-inspect-1.0 libcamerasrc

sudo apt update
sudo apt install libcamera-gstreamer libcamera-tools libcamera-apps -y

gst-launch-1.0 libcamerasrc ! fakesink
gst-launch-1.0 libcamerasrc ! videoconvert ! autovideosink
gst-launch-1.0 libcamerasrc ! video/x-raw,width=1280,height=720,framerate=60/1 ! autovideosink
gst-launch-1.0 libcamerasrc exposure=8000 awb-mode=daylight ! videoconvert ! autovideosink

```